ὲν φ.</quote_> <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0540.tlg007.perseus-grc1:17\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Lys.\">Lys.</a></author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">7.17</biblScope> </bibl> </cit>; <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">μησενὸς ἄλλου φ., πλὴν ὅπως</foreign>. . <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0010.tlg019.perseus-grc1:305\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Isoc.\">Isoc.</a></author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">15.305</biblScope> </bibl>; <cit TEIform=\"cit\"> <quote_ lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"quote\">οὐδὲ τῶν νόμων φροντίζουσι</quote_> <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0059.tlg030.perseus-grc1:563d\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Pl.\">Pl.</a></author> <title_ TEIform=\"title\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ R.\">R.</a></title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">563d</biblScope> </bibl> </cit>; <cit TEIform=\"cit\"> <quote_ lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"quote\">τὸ παράπαν θεῶν μὴ φ.</quote_> <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0059.tlg034.perseus-grc1:701c\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Id.\">Id.</a></author> <title_ TEIform=\"title\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Lg.\">Lg.</a></title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">701c</biblScope> </bibl> </cit>; conversely, <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">τοὺς θεοὺς φ. οὐδὲν τῶν ἀνθρωπίνων</foreign> ib.<bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0059.tlg034.perseus-grc1:888c\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">888c</biblScope></bibl>, cf. <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0541.tlg009:552\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Men.\">Men.</a></author> <title_ TEIform=\"title\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Epit.\">Epit.</a></title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">552</biblScope> </bibl>: so with Advbs. implying a neg., <cit TEI